Checking current version...
 * your/latest build: 8d391c3ad2f0846e9d1366c5d1de5f1b797d799f / 8d391c3ad2f0846e9d1366c5d1de5f1b797d799f
 * build 8d391c3ad2f0846e9d1366c5d1de5f1b797d799f is the latest one.
gallo%
</code></p>

